# Theme & Color System

Dark mode only. Background: super dark gray (`#0A0A0F`–`#111118` range), surface layers progressively lighter for elevation. Not pure black.

## Accent Palette

| Role | Intent | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| **Primary** | Electric blue/indigo | Nav highlights, primary buttons, active states, selected rows |
| **Success** | Vivid teal/green | Pass status, successful ops, positive metrics |
| **Error** | Warm coral/red | Fail status, errors, destructive actions |
| **Warning** | Amber/golden | Blocked status, warnings, thresholds |
| **Info** | Soft violet/purple | Informational badges, automation indicators, links |
| **Neutral** | Cool slate/muted blue-gray | Borders, dividers, secondary text, inactive states |

## Semantic Mappings

**Execution status:** Pass=Success, Fail=Error, Blocked=Warning, Skip=Neutral, Not Run=Neutral(lighter)
**Automation status:** IN CICD=Success, SCRIPTED=Info, OUT OF SYNC=Warning, Not Automated=Neutral
**Platforms:** Desktop=Primary, Tablet=Info, Mobile(future)=Success
**Roles:** Admin=Error, QA Engineer=Primary, SDET=Info, Viewer=Neutral
**Suite colors:** Cycle through Primary→Success→Info→Warning→Error (use `color_index` from suites table)

## Color Rules

- All accents: saturation ~70–85%, brightness tuned for dark background contrast (not neon)
- Raw accent on large surfaces: use at **10–15% opacity** for washes (e.g., selected row background)
- Status badges: accent background at ~20% opacity with full-color text
- All interactive elements: **WCAG AA** contrast (4.5:1 text, 3:1 large text/icons)
- Primary text: `#E8E8ED` range (near-white), secondary text: `#8888A0` range
- Gradients: acceptable for progress bars, charts — subtle, between adjacent palette colors
- Filter chips: filled with the **semantic color of the value being filtered**

## Interactive Elements

- Primary button: filled primary, white text; hover: glow shadow
- Secondary button: outlined primary border, accent text
- Destructive button: filled error, white text
- Link text: Info (violet/purple)
- Selected row: Primary at 15% wash; hovered row: Primary at 8% wash
- Toasts: left border + icon using semantic color (success/error/warning/info)
